Khê kiều tễ nguyệt - 溪橋霽月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/author-IUtlhs85uNhJ4NvGicsgMg">Bùi Huy Bích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A0nh-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-H%C3%B9ng/L%E1%BB%99/poem-FwxfT0d_OcanMENaQOo6jg">Lộ - 露</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A0nh-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-H%C3%B9ng/author-Qv7b3I2-XwrqaKCUV_nCCg">Thành Ngạn Hùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/Ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-b%E1%BA%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%ADt-b%C3%A1n-T%C3%A2y-s%C6%A1n/poem-06QT_9T2e9I52l7ilDATcw">Phú đắc bạch nhật bán Tây sơn - 賦得白日半西山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BA%BFn/author-xOkIiHqP9P6nrS8jJbgRNg">Thường Kiến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Th%E1%BA%BF-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-ti%C3%AAn-nguy%C3%AAn/poem-wJThte8M_J15b8RXy_791A">Thế ngoại tiên nguyên - 世外仙源</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-2-Kh%C3%B4ng-s%C6%A1n-trung-ti%C3%AAu-%C3%A2m/poem-6JwGdfF6cP6pEPkcacvaMg">Vũ kỳ 2 (Không sơn trung tiêu âm) - 雨其二（空山中宵陰）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
